'''加里寧格勒琥珀博物館'''（{{lang-ru|Музей янтаря}}，{{lang-en|Kaliningrad Amber Museum}}）是一座位於[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[加里寧格勒|加里寧格勒]]市專門用於收藏和展示[[琥珀|琥珀]]的[[博物館|博物館]]。它坐落在市中心的Verkhneye湖岸上。<ref name="KAM-Museum">{{Cite web 
 |title=The building of the museum 
 |publisher=Kaliningrad Amber Museum 
 |url=http://www.ambermuseum.ru/museum/building 
 |accessdate=2010-07-03 
 |deadurl=yes 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100817090517/http://www.ambermuseum.ru/museum/building 
 |archivedate=2010-08-17 
 }}</ref>博物館始建于1972年<ref name="KAM-history">{{Cite web 
 |title=Establishment of Museum 
 |publisher=Kaliningrad Amber Museum 
 |url=http://www.ambermuseum.ru/museum/history 
 |accessdate=2010-07-03 
 |deadurl=yes 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100817091350/http://www.ambermuseum.ru/museum/history 
 |archivedate=2010-08-17 
 }}</ref>，開館於1979年，馆藏超過6000件。<ref name="Rice">{{Cite book
  | last = Rice
  | first = Patty D.
  | title = Amber: Golden Gem of the Ages
  | publisher = AuthorHouse
  | date = 2006
  | pages = 119
  | url = http://books.google.com.au/books?id=g6NVVpqhixIC&pg=PA119&dq=%22Kaliningrad+Amber+Museum%22&hl=en&ei=0JMuTKmgH4-gkQWb0O2CBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22Kaliningrad%20Amber%20Museum%22&f=false
  | isbn = 1-4259-3849-3
  | access-date = 2013-07-13
  | archive-date = 2012-11-04
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104002325/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=g6NVVpqhixIC&pg=PA119&dq=%22Kaliningrad+Amber+Museum%22&hl=en&ei=0JMuTKmgH4-gkQWb0O2CBA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22Kaliningrad%20Amber%20Museum%22&f=false
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>該博物館位于一座重建的[[條頓|條頓]]城堡中，占用了城堡的一部分。<ref name="Rice"/>这座城堡最初由{{link-en|卡爾·弗里德里希·埃米爾·祖·多納·施洛比滕|Karl Friedrich Emil zu Dohna-Schlobitten}}在[[拿破崙戰爭|拿破崙戰爭]]期间建造。<ref name="KAM-Museum"/>

展品中包括世界第二大的琥珀<ref>{{Cite book
